{"tid":1990384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透社：中國外交官去信德國　要求發放中方應對疫情正面資訊　德無配合要求","createTime":"2020-04-26T15:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T15:46:59.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6c75e1f8eb93affc5a99fa47020dd02fb972b440","tid":1990384,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎在全球大流行，中國過去被指公布疫情的透明度不足。《路透社》取得德國內政部一封信件，信中提及中國曾提出要求，鼓勵德國就北京如何處理冠狀病毒大流行發表積極聲明。<br />\n<br />\n該信件日期是 4 月 22 日，是內政部回應綠黨國會議員Margarete Bause，有關中國外交官與德國政府官員接觸的查詢。報道指，德國政府沒有配合有關要求，強調德國肯定中國應對疫情的努力，並告訴中國政府保持透明度很重要。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐柏林大使館及中國外交部，暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/路透社-中國外交官去信德國-要求發放中方應對疫情正面資訊-德無配合要求/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E5%AE%98%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%99%BC%E6%94%BE%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%A2%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A-%E5%BE%B7%E7%84%A1%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%2F&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4JktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=cc3cd031\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E5%AE%98%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%99%BC%E6%94%BE%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%A2%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A-%E5%BE%B7%E7%84%A1%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%2F&h=7c8cb3b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/路透社-中國外交官去信德國-要求發放中方應對疫情正面資訊-德無配合要求/</a>"},{"pid":"b83daec5aa2584e8a19fa224cb4e47b91b57db00","tid":1990384,"uid":321803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:46:59.000Z","msg":"你比舊屎我食仲要多謝你<br />\n行撚開啦 nmsl"}]}